Step 1. Beginning

Create a blank window. Pressing a `q` key terminates the program.

Step 2. 3D model

Draw a polygons model from a some simple input file.

Step 3. Controls

Make control with mouse and keyboard.

Step 4. Game logic

Do some logic on scene. Object must moving without user interaction.

Step 6. Sound

Create a sound effects.

Step 5. Simple 2D world

Do a simple 2D world with moving objects and controls.
